Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.21,0:01:17.62,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,O flower, parched in the light of dawn,{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.85,0:01:21.30,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,reaching for the unfallen rain,{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.30,0:01:28.35,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,fall into a wakeless sleep.{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.90,0:01:42.26,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone calls out softly for a paradise of darkness.{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.26,0:01:43.91,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a lie or a dream?{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.91,0:01:46.00,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, it's already lost.{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.00,0:01:52.06,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you gain by putting forth your heart?{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.41,0:01:56.13,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,Looking through those eyes,{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:59.23,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,life is foolish and fleeting enough to snatch away.{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:02.76,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,Will today be the day you grieve the end{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:05.97,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,which comes to us all?{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.97,0:02:09.57,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,The calendula which sings of the abyss{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.57,0:02:13.23,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,silently blooms full.{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:16.40,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatred and sadness{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.40,0:02:20.11,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,are bound together in those eyes.{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:23.25,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,The calendula which sings of demise{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:26.86,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,is watered by solitude,{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.86,0:02:30.10,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,reaching for the unfallen rain,{\be1\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.10,0:02:36.53,OPKara,,0000,0000,0000,,fall into a wakeless sleep.{\be1\fad(200,1000)}
